            "title": "油價靠穩　市場評估供應收緊及貿易戰風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際油價延續上日升勢，投資者評估原油供應收緊及貿易戰風險，憂慮關稅措施或令石油需求減少。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報69.92美元，升27美仙，升幅約0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶74.03美元，升24美仙，升幅0.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14810742-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e9%9d%a0%e7%a9%a9%e3%80%80%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e8%a9%95%e4%bc%b0%e4%be%9b%e6%87%89%e6%94%b6%e7%b7%8a%e5%8f%8a%e8%b2%bf%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0%e9%a2%a8%e9%9a%aa-2",
